Private Parts

Health-Medical Documentary published by Channel 5  in 2006 - English narration


Information
------------------------------

Three-part documentary series looking at human breasts and genitals and problems associated with them experienced by some people. GB. Five tx 2006/05/15-2006/05/29


1)  The Trouble With My Breasts 
Documentary about the women whose breasts have landed them in hospital, out of a job, with a lawsuit, and in a Greek prison.


2)  The Trouble With My Vagina 
Documentary revealing some of the dangers of the new post-&#039;Sex in the City&#039; frankness about female sexuality - from Brazilian waxing accidents to designer vagina surgeries gone wrong.


3)  The Trouble With My Penis 
A man&#039;s sense of self is deeply rooted in his member. This documentary explores how this can get him in trouble, from piercings gone wrong and misjudged self-treatments for impotence to sexual encounters that ended in pain rather than pleasure.
